

Code repository to replicate Auclert, A., Bardóczy, B., Rognlie, M., & Straub, L. (2021). Using the sequence‐space Jacobian to solve and estimate heterogeneous‐agent models. Econometrica, 89(5), 2375-2408.

- ssj.m computes fake new matrix and replicates figure 2. Also computes general equilibrium response.

- KSsteady.m computes model steady state which inputs to ssj.m [no need to resolve]

